                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Diplomatic Agent <persName type="to">Jackson</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <hi rend="italic">
                            <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-09-24">September 24, 1906</date>
                        </hi>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Informs him that the President signed, September 15, a proclamation of a
                    commercial arrangement with Bulgaria, to take effect September 30. States that a
                    formal exchange of notes may be made reciting date if practicable. Reply to his
                    telegram of September 18.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
